Instead of just indicators, it looks for behavioral patterns in price:

1️⃣ Liquidity sweep

Example:
• Price breaks a previous low
• Triggers stop losses
• Then quickly reverses upward

That often signals smart money accumulation.

2️⃣ Trend alignment

Only trades with the larger trend using the 200 EMA.

3️⃣ Volatility-adaptive exits

Stops and targets use ATR, which adapts to market volatility
